snippet.title: PlayStation - KuruKuru MaruMaru (2001) - Intro
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
KuruKuru MaruMaru is an Action game, developed by Japan Art Media (JAM) and published by Hudson, which was released in Japan in 2001.
